{"tid":1969692,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大嶼村民堵羌山道","createTime":"2020-04-12T15:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T15:15:54.000Z","uid":30788,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f36db7dd423af8058e348c22f0368066aff7a0d7","tid":1969692,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:03:11.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】逾百名大嶼山居民不滿政府多年來漠視區內道路問題，日前一度堵塞羌山道抗議。沙螺灣村村長李秀梅昨日在一個電台節目中警告，不排除再發起村民到場「視察交通」，意味堵路行動陸續有來。她指出，羌山道彎多路窄，七三年發生巴士墮崖意外後，多年來從無改善，村民及遊客每天出入均是冒着生命危險，她更隔空質問運輸及房屋局局長張炳良，一旦再發生同類意外，「點同國際（社會）交代」？"},{"pid":"2c1076f18d414a778ece36cbb729336095e535a7","tid":1969692,"uid":103981,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"張炳良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1369f28c320d904bcca814ed782a5eaa90ad3757","tid":1969692,"uid":214036,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:04:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4e503cc0e1ca004ac12e40690679b153603a40a","tid":1969692,"uid":200070,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"D村咁暴力 郁D堵路既"},{"pid":"d401039cdfee05e906e8f1db1471a9198d25412e","tid":1969692,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:08:44.000Z","msg":"住得喺呢啲地方預咗交通唔好啦下話"},{"pid":"fb6677df8b5741e43f5d9294cb7207aa7d111234","tid":1969692,"uid":337899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:09:51.000Z","msg":"大嶼山獨立"},{"pid":"48f0db69c58d23592495d02cc042d7304a57f867","tid":1969692,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"塞自己? 山卡啦有鬼人入去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c455bdadc5586511011600f41b895d0db8a5f3","tid":1969692,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c1076f18d414a778ece36cbb729336095e535a7","tid":1969692,"uid":103981,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020